displayName: Medicine Town Medicina, Home of the Pharmacist Piton

parameters:
Pharmacist Piton: You came...!? You look like a different
person, it's confusing, go back.
Pharmacist Piton: Who are you guys?
Clea: I came to see the request form from Kanonas.

Pharmacist Piton: Kanonas...!? That bastard sent it to the
wrong place...
Pharmacist Piton: Well... it's about the snake incident...

Thief Nora: If it's something you're looking for, leave it

Pharmacist Piton: Ah, ah... I want you to search separately,
please stay here.

Clea: By the way, may I ask for more details about the
snake?

Clea: If you could tell me the color, shape, size, and other
characteristics, it would make the investigation easier.

Pharmacist Piton: Sigh... It seems like you really don't

Clea: Hey, what are you taking out...!? P-Please put it away

Pharmacist Piton: It was just a small mistake. I was

Pharmacist Piton: You really are an ignorant young lady. The

Pharmacist Piton: It's a code word for calling a prostitute.
This town is strict, so I intended to ask Valie for help.

Pharmacist Piton: After explaining all this, are you going

Clea: The giant snake has become smaller. We can crush it,

Pharmacist Piton: Ugh, ugh... F-Fine, the request is over...
damn it...!

Pharmacist Piton: Here's some pocket change, take it! I like

Pharmacist Piton: I know, you came without knowing. I won't
insert anything.

Pharmacist Piton: You have a good body hidden under that

Clea: Understood... If that's what you want.

Pharmacist Piton: Take off that unsightly armor and show me
your beautiful body already.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Pharmacist Piton: What a magnificent chest! I have to thank

Clea: Please give me my reward.

Pharmacist Piton: I understand. Here, I'll give you some

Pharmacist Piton: If you feel like earning money again, come
back. This town doesn't have much entertainment to spend
money on, so I'll pay you generously, okay?

Pharmacist Piton: You came...!? You look different, it's

Pharmacist Piton: I'm looking forward to seeing you again.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

Pharmacist Piton: The snake is in a bad mood... I'll use
